<div class="title">Advice for the Curious</div>
<div class="substance">Proteus Mind Machine & 2C-I</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=lucidinthesky&Exact=1">lucidinthesky</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; lucidinthesky. "Advice for the Curious: An Experience with Proteus Mind Machine & 2C-I (exp30962)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 16, 2004. erowid.org/exp/30962</div>

